                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270405-259-off1416 t18270405-259-cd1417"></join>, 30 lbs. weight of iron, value 1s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18270405-259-victim1449" type="victimName">
                  George 
